Package: countrows
Title: Count Rows Matching a Pattern Using grep
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Aastik", "Narang", , "aastik839@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a function to count rows in a data frame that match a
    given pattern. It efficiently leverages the system's 'grep -c' command by
    writing the data to a temporary file, avoiding loading potentially large
    matched data into R.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
